    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who construct models, generally from hard, nonmalleable materials such as wood or stone, such as scale working or display models of three-dimensional objects or models to produce molds for cast products. For those who create models of clay, wax, or other malleable material, see "modelers".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000096613/Museum of Modern Art (MoMA), New York [online] (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aquellos que construyen modelos, tales como trabajos a escala o modelos de exhibición de objetos tridimensionales o modelos para producir moldes para productos vaciados. Para los que fabrican modelos de arcilla, de cera, o de otro material maleable, ver a "modelista”.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Zij die doorgaans van harde, niet-plooibare materialen zoals hout of steen modellen bouwen, bijvoorbeeld werkende modellen of showmodellen op schaal, van driedimensionale objecten, of modellen waarmee mallen voor gegoten producten worden geproduceerd. Zie 'modelleurs' voor mensen die modellen maken van klei, was of andere pletbare materialen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
